NAME

  IOas::CP932 - provides CP932 I/O subroutines for UTF-8 script

SYNOPSIS

  use IOas::CP932;

DESCRIPTION

  IOas::CP932 module provides CP932 I/O subroutines for UTF-8 script for
  stable scripting environment, using no utf8 pragma, no UTF-8 flag.

SUBROUTINES

  Octet Length as I/O Encoding
    IOas::CP932::length($utf8str)
    IOas::CP932::sprintf($utf8format, @utf8list)
    IOas::CP932::substr($utf8expr, $offset_as_cp932x, $length_as_cp932x, $utf8replacement)

  String Comparison as I/O Encoding
    IOas::CP932::cmp($utf8str_a, $utf8str_b)
    IOas::CP932::eq($utf8str_a, $utf8str_b)
    IOas::CP932::ne($utf8str_a, $utf8str_b)
    IOas::CP932::ge($utf8str_a, $utf8str_b)
    IOas::CP932::gt($utf8str_a, $utf8str_b)
    IOas::CP932::le($utf8str_a, $utf8str_b)
    IOas::CP932::lt($utf8str_a, $utf8str_b)
    IOas::CP932::sort(@utf8str)

  Encoding Convert on I/O Operations
    IOas::CP932::getc(FILEHANDLE)
    IOas::CP932::readline(FILEHANDLE)
    IOas::CP932::print(FILEHANDLE, @utf8str)
    IOas::CP932::printf(FILEHANDLE, $utf8format, @utf8list)

SUPPORTED PERL VERSIONS

  perl version 5.005_03 to newest perl

SEE ALSO

  http://search.cpan.org/~ina/
